  "original_title": "22 \u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "22 train services canceled today",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Railways has announced that 22 trains scheduled to operate today (July 01) have been canceled.",
        "According to the Railway Department, 22 train services have been canceled due to lack of staff.",
        "It is reported that the train services have been canceled due to the railway employees not being able to socialize for work due to the traffic problems caused due to the fuel crisis.",
        "According to the Department of Railways, the canceled train services include some trains plying on the office train service."
      ],
